Package android.support.v17.leanback.supportleanbackshowcase.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    This is a generic example of a custom data object, containing info we might want to keep with each card on the home screen
    CardListRow
    The CardListRow allows the ShadowRowPresenterSelector to access the CardRow held by the row and determine whether to use a Presenter with or without a shadow.
    CardRow
    This class represents a row of cards.
    DetailedCard
    A more detailed data object than Card, to be used in details view i.e., DetailViewActivity.
    IconHeaderItem
    A child class of HeaderItem, an object to display header title with a custom icon besides it.
